  "strategy": [
    "Commit to actions (move, rotate, scan) until a significant event occurs (obstacle, marker_seen, marker_close).",
    "After every forward commit, perform a scan (full_rotate) to improve marker detection and avoid long straight runs.",
    "Use rotate commit states to avoid oscillations and ensure persistent turning until path is clear.",
    "On obstacle detection, recover by backing up or rotating, then scan before resuming forward.",
    "When marker_seen, immediately commit to move_to_marker; do not return to exploration unless marker is lost.",
    "When marker_close, stop to safely complete the approach.",
    "All uncontrollable events are handled in every state to ensure robustness.",
    "Exploration alternates between short forward moves and scans to maximize marker acquisition speed."
  ]
